org.mitre.provenance.user

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.PLUSActor
      • org.mitre.provenance.user.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Neo4JCapable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OpenIDUser

    public class User
extends PLUSActor
    A PLUS User, that is, an individual or organization using the provenance system. It is extended from PLUSActor because users themselves can participate in provenance graphs.
    Author:
    DMALLEN
